## About This Repository

This repository contains Jupyter Notebooks for analysis of Command-an-Control (C2 or C&C) communications across the network.

## Requirements and Installation

- Jupyter Notebooks and JupyterLab: [**link**](https://jupyter.org/install)

## Usage

Just spin up your JupyterLab and access it from your web browser.  
If you like using WSL and VisualStudio Code from Windows you can follow the documentation [**here**](https://code.visualstudio.com/blogs/2019/09/03/wsl2) and [**here**](https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/datascience/jupyter-notebooks).

## List of Notebooks

|Notebook|Purpose|
|-|-|
|dns.ipynb|Hunt C2 over DNS|
